      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Check out this dependable driver with tons of personality! It's in fair condition and ready to hit the road today. While it shows some honest signs of its age\u2014including some cosmetic wear and minor mechanical quirks that could use a little attention\u2014it remains a solid, functional vehicle perfect for someone who appreciates a car with a story. It's a great opportunity to own a classic that you can drive and enjoy while you gradually make it your own!",
