    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she's been a total dream. This car has been well-loved and is in really wonderful shape, running smoothly and looking great both inside and out. It\u2019s the perfect reliable companion for your daily commutes or weekend adventures. I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you're going to love driving it as much as I have! Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 32500.0,
