      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sorted E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit delivers exceptional throttle response through its six individual throttle bodies and is paired with a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul to ensure optimal cam timing and torque delivery. The chassis retains its signature balance with a functional variable M differential lock and refreshed suspension bushings. While the exterior shows minor stone chipping and light interior bolster wear, the drivetrain and structural integrity are excellent, making this a driver-focused example ready for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
